{"tid":559364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女同事擺出這姿勢　網友問：該撿東西嗎","createTime":"2018-02-13T06:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T06:55:11.000Z","uid":72009,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03825f848289beee9d261f95ef1ec29dccdcba58","tid":559364,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"網友在臉書社團爆廢公社分享照片，一名身穿窄裙、黑絲襪的女同事，半倚在辦公桌前，與其他同事討論事情，身形誘人。<br />\n他問：「要蹲下去撿東西嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n想也知道太低級了，原PO被網友臭幹一番，痛批他沒水準。<br />\n但仍有網友希望認識照片中的女生，「我可以私訊她以後不要穿這麼短」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180213/640_169a7b41bba3266957b2227a7476d29e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180213%2F640_169a7b41bba3266957b2227a7476d29e.jpg&h=5c83bfc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台仔天天想做愛是有原因"},{"pid":"ee8b63631b6720507f5dc6bed8d6e9e1e30ad8f5","tid":559364,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"新北市嗎"},{"pid":"70517a6d68d90f70a9e4e9ef019ba89e0f203739","tid":559364,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"隻腳打乜撚嘢格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf09862aa9c9e1f459cc9cd480312f1df055586a","tid":559364,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70517a6d68d90f70a9e4e9ef019ba89e0f203739","tid":559364,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"隻腳打乜撚嘢格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"f5bb5196e8e3082aa2753652b9f44ab0c3de8296","tid":559364,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf09862aa9c9e1f459cc9cd480312f1df055586a","tid":559364,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70517a6d68